title: Bliss
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Western, Buffet, Salad bar, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Bakery, European
description: Offers a daily buffet with 100+ items including raw, gluten and lactose free. There's also a cake and desserts case. Sources non-gmo ingredients. Bright, modern interior with plenty of seating. Free Wi-Fi and parking zone. Opened early-2014.
